 we answer some of the questions that are coming. 

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:17.400
 How do you get here? 

00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:19.360
 PAUL: coming here is actually very simple 

00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:21.420
 It's not difficult. There is no 

00:00:21.420 --> 00:00:24.360
 drama. It is as simple as 

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:26.660
 organizing an excursion on a normal holiday. 

00:00:26.660 --> 00:00:28.000
 About. There are some 

