 A dark corridor ... 

00:08:13.460 --> 00:08:17.060
 A few mailboxes, a kind of pigeon hole with colors ... 

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:20.920
 A gust of wind came along and that all creaked at once 

00:08:20.920 --> 00:08:23.160
 And I thought I saw something at the end of the corridor 

