 TOM: Ok, maybe I was not in a situation where that happened 

00:08:29.340 --> 00:08:31.120
 PAUL: Seconds later, absolutely fine 

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:34.280
 TOM: Cause, I do not know. Middle of winter, dead of the night 

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:37.180
 When it gets cold and inclement and dark and rainy 

00:08:37.180 --> 00:08:40.240
 Yes, then I understand. But we were here in the middle of summer 

